title: Are There Two Unreleased Beatles Songs?
subtitle: Rumor has it that the Beatles recorded the songs 'Colliding Circles' and 'Pink Litmus Paper Shirt' which remain unreleased to this day.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: The Beatles recorded songs entitled "Colliding Circles," "Left Is Right (And Right Is Wrong)," "Pink Litmus Paper Shirt," and "Deckchair," all of which remain unreleased to this day.
